Package: python3-rkwhisper-client
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Python client for the rkwhisper speech recognition daemon
 Python bindings for the rkwhisper ASR daemon built with PyO3 and Maturin.
 Provides synchronous and asynchronous session types for streaming audio to
 rkwhisperd and receiving transcription segments in real time.
